data.description: Beautifully updated split level home. 4-5 bedrooms, 3 full bathes. Open floor plan. Hardwood, ceramic tile, LVT  downstairs. One year old new HVAC. New garage door openers. Beautifully decorated with many updates. Beautiful wooded 0.89 acre lot, large double carport. Near great schools. Call 706-270-2392 for an appointment to come and see. You won't be disappointed!
data.whatILove: Provides a wonderful woodsy atmosphere, yet close enough to Dalton and Chattanooga you can be there in mere minutes.  Great schools.
